title: The Lost Princess  of Oz
creator: L. Frank Baum
description: LibriVox recording of The Lost Princess of Oz, by L. Frank Baum. Read by Mark F. Smith. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. Download M4B (144MB)
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text

reviews.reviewbody: This is not my favorite Oz book. But the reading was so lively and novel that I enjoyed it greatly.
